為pure math底嘅人學programming段而仲辛苦，因為pure math係抽象嘅，係直接學個theory，從底層直理學上去，但programming 係相反，佢哋嘅學習比d散手手嘅例子去學，去歸納佢哋嘅知識庫。用學捉棋做例，pure math係直接base on 棋規去deduced d棋理/技巧，所以就算唔洗點捉棋，捉棋嘅實力都可以提升；cs人學棋就偏向實戰捉棋，再會捉個時遇到嘅事，去歸納出技巧。<br />\n<br />\n而因為咁，所以坊間大部電腦教programming 嘅書都係先比段code你，再講段code點解，對d pure math就會覺得「做乜鳩，你連d syntax 點解，佢對電腦做緊d咩都未講就比例子」。"},{"pid":"1b27d51957d2a7748e847758554e9f7ca2fd4afb","tid":2500832,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:47:17.000Z","msg":"睇寫乜，咩image processing, robotics, machine learning呢啲就應該有既，始終入面個algorithm點嚟係based on一啲數學/統計理論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e444b2b19287a3592d626c672fc1e0930d772f0d","tid":2500832,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40eb4d467bc1cd1c9b144ac6da1bcb9bdce69cdd","tid":2500832,"uid":139200,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:10:57.000Z","msg":"CS<br />\n兩大領域 tech knowledge &amp; dup code<br />\n<br />\n數底好 tech 果堆logic<br />\n會易理解d<br />\n<br />\nDup code就個個一樣<br />\nDup得多先會熟..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:47:33.000Z","msg":"Tech knowledge 多少係睇下你對讀書興趣幾大<br />\n倒如新language 新framework要係咁睇片睇教學先識<br />\nMath勁但唔肯睇呢啲應該會同樓主差唔多情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d459afb283d8169dc9185447fa17dba469a7e6","tid":2500832,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:49:55.000Z","msg":"唔駛諗咁多 數學/code是但一樣廢 就係廢柴<br />\n<br />\n利申 引戰"},{"pid":"8575fd80db2e0e97227ccfb08abf0e787005c066","tid":2500832,"uid":193131,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:52:05.000Z","msg":"數學撚太執著果啲嚴謹的邏輯<br />\n但programming 好多時都係歸納例子去學習，解決問題為主"},{"pid":"5ef3f183a1f30977a51665d007c44a00788ba567","tid":2500832,"uid":224545,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:56:05.000Z","msg":"毒撚＞ 操數＞數學叻<br />\n毒撚＞操code&gt;program叻"},{"pid":"3153fd62c9ccdc673db20120fdf2c5d0e18ef7f6","tid":2500832,"uid